{"tid":1185233,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"澳洲央行宣布減息25個基點符預期 澳元不跌反升","createTime":"2019-06-04T06:56:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-04T08:07:44.000Z","uid":67792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"da5e55d9e3d7274248c8b45ad4b971068459c371","tid":1185233,"uid":67792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T06:56:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-con/NOW.944887/top-news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-con%2FNOW.944887%2Ftop-news&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgtmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=30304e34\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-con/NOW.944887/top-news</a><br />\n澳洲央行宣布減息25個基點，將指標利率降至1.25厘，為自2016年8月以來首次減息。<br />\n受到基礎設施投資的增加和資源開採活動上升所支持，央行維持預期今明兩年經濟增長為2.75%。不過，家庭消費前景仍然具不確定因素，因為房價下跌及工資增長慢，將繼續拖累家庭消費。<br />\n央行維持今年核心通脹預測為1.75%，明年為2%，之後通脹料會略為向上。<br />\n消息公布後，澳元兌美元不跌反升，最新報0.6987。<br />\n<br />\n代表D咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e47561b091204eeb5a5f8050c2951e6627f0479d","tid":1185233,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da5e55d9e3d7274248c8b45ad4b971068459c371","tid":1185233,"uid":67792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-04T06:56:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-con/NOW.944887/top-news\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fstocks%2Fnews%2Faafn-con%2FNOW.944887%2Ftop-news&d=nhC78NoCA6QB0w8lKR9CgtmOP5%2FvN4RyP%2Fy1e26q30o%3D&h=30304e34\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/stocks/news/aafn-con/NOW.944887/top-news</a><br />\n澳洲央行宣布減息25個基點，將指標利率降至1.25厘，為自2016年8月以來首次減息。<br />\n受到基礎設施投資的增加和資源開採活動上升所支持，央行維持預期今明兩年經濟增長為2.75%。不過，家庭消費前景仍然具不確定因素，因為房價下跌及工資增長慢，將繼續拖累家庭消費。<br />\n央行維持今年核心通脹預測為1.75%，明年為2%，之後通脹料會略為向上。<br />\n消息公布後，澳元兌美元不跌反升，最新報0.6987。<br />\n<br />\n代表D咩？<img src